data.description: Darling home in charming Kuna community. This home features three bedroom two bathroom split bedroom design with large entryway & mud room w/ built in bench. Take in this open concept in main living area with vaulted ceilings in great room, newer hardwood throughout kitchen, dining room, hallways, entry & new carpet in great room. Spacious kitchen features granite counter tops, pantry, island, fridge & stainless steel appliances in kitchen! Master offers dual vanities, shower, bath tub, & separate toilet area. This home is better then new with blinds, full landscape & fencing, fridge, washer & dryer & newer water softener all included! Come see this darling home today!
